    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>ParagnaLL12.3.6 Var. a (Ms. K36):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> OD <em>tā̊scā yaz</em> esm va buy yektā ke nahāde bar u ātaš nahešn</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "(He should recite) <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> until <em>tā̊scā yaz</em>. He has to put onto the fire one piece of the <em>esm</em> and <em>buy</em> that has been prepared
                onto the fire."</ab>
            
            <ab>ParagnaLL12.3.6 Var. b (RJ, K7):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> tā sar u fe <em>yā̊ŋhąmcā</em> ān esm va buy yek tāk farāǧ u ātaš barešn"</ab> 
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "(He should recite) <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> until the end and at <em>tā̊scā yaz</em> he has to bring one piece of <em>esm</em> and <em>buy</em> to the fire."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
